\[\text{Var}[\widehat{\text{ATE}}_{\text{IPW}}]-\text{Var}[\widehat{\text{ATE }}_{\text{MR}}]=\frac{1}{n}\left(\text{Var}[\rho_{\text{ATE}}(A,X)\,Y]-\text{ Var}[w_{\text{ATE}}(Y)\,Y]\right).\] (9)

